3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of probabilistic models to estimate fitness, which is a common technique used in machine learning. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the effect of fitness inheritance on convergence time and population sizing, which are important aspects of algorithm design. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper proposes a technique to improve the efficiency of genetic algorithms, which is relevant to software engineering applications that involve optimization problems.
